---
title: Pan-Fried Gilt Bream with Zesty Toasted Coconut Jasmine Rice, Roasted Tenderstem® and Miso Dressing
description: We love a good Seabass with Rice & Miso Dressing and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
